# 1. Types of network
LAN (Local Area Network) connect local devices together within a single location or site.

WAN (Wide Area Network) connects LANs together over large geographic distances, often using public networks like the Internet

What type of network is a computer in local connected to?

LAN
What type of network could connect an office in one building to another office in a building a few streets away?

WAN
What network do you use when you browse www.google.com from your smartphone (not connected to the Wifi)?

Internet

